		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="#regest1">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et vitae innocentiam a domino.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bonus hic senecio<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Unbekannt.</note> caussam habet matrimonialem, in qua ipsi tua intelligo opus esse opera.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fidem enim dedit filia Geysmeyeri<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Wohl <persName ref="943">Margareta Geißmeyer</persName>, die Tochter von <persName ref="944">Michael Geißmeyer</persName> (s. Emil <hi>Stauber,</hi> Geschichte der Kirchgemeinde Andelfingen, Bd. II, Zürich 1941, S. 889).</note> a Gyrspurg<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><placeName ref="405">Girsberg</placeName> (Waltalingen, Kt. Zürich).</note> filio<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Unbekannt.</note> suo.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc, quantum intelligo, dissimulat et facta infecta esse vellet.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu vero pro tua pietate nosti fidem pactam maxime in nuptiis atque sponsalibus non temere solvendam esse.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dabis ergo operam, ut commonita offitii sui caveat, ne conscientiam perfidia polluat.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Modica scintillula in fomitem recondita conscientiae incredibile<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>in der Vorlage</hi> incredebile.</note> aliquando excitabit homini incendium<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Vgl. Otto 311f, Nr. 1604.</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Credidit fortasse delatoribus nimis credula puella.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si fidem dedit, credat deo magis<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">magis <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note> et stet pactis.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non audio quicquam hic inscia matre<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Wohl <persName ref="942">Magdalena Geißmeyer</persName> (s. <hi>Stauber,</hi> aaO, S. 889).</note> actum esse.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fortassis filiae poenitentiam nescit.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Prudenter tamen ista omnia inquires.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri, 9. septembris anno 1537.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod autem huic seni impenderis diligentiae, mihi putabo impensum.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">H. Bullingerus tuus.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName ref="151">Laurentio Agricolae</persName>, Stamheymensi pastori vigilantissimo et longe charissimo fratri.</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
